    <p>The <link xref="bson_destroy">bson_destroy()</link> function shall free an allocated <link xref="bson_t">bson_t</link> structure.</p>
    <p>This function should always be called when you are done with a <link xref="bson_t">bson_t</link> unless otherwise specified.</p>
